wikipedia_page.main: Lauren Walker (born 12 March 1989) is an English footballer who usually plays at either left-back or left midfield. She currently plays for Sporting Khalsa, and previously represented Blackburn Rovers Ladies in the FA Women's Premier League National Division. She hails from Birches Head, Staffordshire.
